==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Observing
<hw>Ob*serv"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Giving particular attention;
habitually attentive to what passes; observant{1}; <as>as, an
<ex>observing</ex> person; an <ex>observing</ex> mind.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>Ob*serv"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>obsess</ent>⟦br⟧
